title: Alberta Finance Minister Joe Ceci to unveil Q3 budget numbers
text:
February 23, 2017 10:02 am Updated: February 23, 2017 10:05 am Alberta Finance Minister Joe Ceci to unveil Q3 budget numbers By Staff The Canadian Press 
WATCH ABOVE: Alberta has a multi-billion dollar deficit. Next door in British Columbia, the government tabled its fifth straight balanced budget. It has some asking if Alberta could learn a lesson from our neighbours to the west. Tom Vernon looks at the numbers. What is this?
